data.description: AN EXCEPTIONAL, IDEALLY SITUATED HOME WITH 4 BEDROOMS & 3 FULL BATHS, NESTLED IN THE COVETED NORTHWEST, PRAIRIE PONDS SUBDIVISION IN PLAINFIELD, AWAITS YOU!  FEATURING HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGHOUT THE MAIN LEVEL AND AN IMPRESSIVE HARDWOOD STAIRCASE LEADING TO THE UPPER LEVEL AS YOU ENTER THROUGH THE FRONT FOYER.  NATURAL LIGHT IS ABUNDANT THROUGHOUT THE HOME ALONG WITH A WARM AND INVITING FLOOR PLAN.  A BREATHTAKING FAMILY ROOM WITH 2 STORY HIGH CEILINGS AND A STONE FINISHED FIREPLACE IS READY TO CUDDLE YOU IN ON THOSE COLD WINTER NIGHTS.  THE CONVENIENT MAIN FLOOR OFFICE, FINISHED WITH BEAUTIFUL WOODWORK, WILL SATISFY ALL YOUR WORK-FROM-HOME NEEDS.  DON'T FORGET THE READY-TO-ENTERTAIN BRICK PAVERED PATIO WITH AN OUTDOOR KITCHEN AND GRANITE COUNTERTOPS THAT WILL SURELY DELIGHT ALL YOUR GUESTS.  THERE'S PLENTY OF PARKING WITH A 3 CAR GARAGE, DRIVEWAY AND STREET.  SO COME TOUR THIS 5,000 PLUS SQUARE FOOT HOME SITTING ON OVER 16,000 SQUARE FEET OF LAND!
